On 22nd of June, 2024, my first novel, "Dance in The Windstorm" released at Title Waves Bookstore, Bandra, Mumbai This story has been a passion project for years, and I'm so excited to finally share it with the world. The book is a classic horror fiction that has elements of adventure. Are you ready to get swept away by "Dance in the Windstorm"?
